from jhpb joseph h buehler subject re the doctrine of original sin regarding the consequence of the original sin catholic believe that what adam primarily lose by hi sin for himself and the human race wa sanctify grace thi be basically a share in the divine life take a rock and make it able to talk what god do to a human be through sanctify grace be similar it make such a one able to live on a plane that be above the power of any possible creature thi be the everlasting life that the new testament speak of what christ do when he come wa to restore thi life of sanctify grace to the human race he institute the sacrament a the mean by which thi life be give to person and it increase foster the absence of sanctify grace at death mean automatic exclusion from heaven the nature of heaven be such that it impossible for a human be to have any part in it without the gift of sanctify grace to use my example it would be like take that rock and attempt to hold a conversation with it rock can not talk neither can human be live in heaven without sanctify grace thi all obviously apply equally well to infant or adult since both have soul infant must be baptize therefore or they can not enter into heaven they too need thi form of life in them or they can not enter into heaven turning it around infant baptism be good support evidence for the catholic belief in sanctify grace unles baptism cause some change in an infant soul there be no particular reason to insist on the practice yet infant baptism wa probably practice by the apostle themself and wa certainly part of the church shortly thereafter there be evidence for infant baptism in the new testament itself cor act also act it be know for sure that at least one disciple of the apostle john wa baptize a an infant st polycarp because of a remark he make in the act of hi martyrdom st justin martyr mention man and woman baptize a infant there be direct evidence in st irenaeu against heresy and in tertullian on baptism all these so far mention be in the first year after my lord death after that there start to be ton of evidence for the practice 